口述实录 | 我在武汉方舱医院14天，有了一种胜利在望的感觉。
At Wuhan Fang Cavern Hospital for 14 days, I had a feeling of victory in sight.
余毅；王仲昀。
Yu Yi; Wang Zhongyun.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
新民周刊。
Xinmin Weekly.
深度和角度——这就是我们能做的。
Depth and angle - that's what we can do.
